{"tid":674962,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Trivago d 酒店咁平，究竟點樣回到本","createTime":"2018-05-23T06:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T07:42:57.000Z","uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b915e3cc15274c3ae4621ef421f54b698c2442ac","tid":674962,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"每次search 酒店都有專人幫我搵哂所有網站價錢<br />\n仲要三十秒内就search 到<br />\n保守估計起馬一team 人大約二十個先有咁嘅效率<br />\n我試過用電話ipad 同時search 兩間唔同酒店<br />\ne 次就慢左d 大約要三十至四十秒 先出哂<br />\n不過咁樣證明左間公司唔只得一條team 同時做野<br />\n最後搵到d 酒店又平又靚 真係服左佢間公司d 員工<br />\n保守估計佢香港分公司應該要around 一千人營運<br />\n但我好奇香港真係咁多人去旅行咩<br />\n酒店又平 究竟Trivago 點回本"},{"pid":"7c6e4b24a01062398828525ae5c757fe8ec9d1cc","tid":674962,"uid":92611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"打手?"},{"pid":"ab1d0105c0775654968a1e0f0047ad7956ae94fd","tid":674962,"uid":173272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"旦求打過和，大家開開心心"},{"pid":"a2b78a722f927056ca52a28f56d4f9173cb4350e","tid":674962,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈"},{"pid":"fb1e757c6f2e4085231dffe34c777fe860a8c625","tid":674962,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0045dbf194b3f566aae04e216da8338505da1736","tid":674962,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"打和囉，問黎多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bea9e93c88c031681d3a65391faf1f7721474b","tid":674962,"uid":112742,"like":4,"dislike":1